section: Provider Signatories
---
signline: Authorized Signatory | name: {{provider_signer_1}} | role: {{provider_role_1}} | date: true
signline: Witness | name: {{provider_witness}} | role: {{provider_witness_role}} | date: true
---
section: Client Signatories
---
signline: Authorized Signatory | name: {{client_signer_1}} | role: {{client_role_1}} | date: true
signline: Authorized Signatory | name: {{client_signer_2}} | role: {{client_role_2}} | date: true
signline: Witness | name: {{client_witness}} | role: {{client_witness_role}} | date: true
---
section: Execution
---
paragraph: By signing above, each signatory represents that they have the authority to bind their respective organization to the terms of the Agreement.
